data.description: Welcome to your ideal starter home and investment opportunity! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is nestled on a spacious lot, presenting a perfect blend of comfort and potential. Located in a prime spot near Hobby Airport and just a stone's throw away from downtown Houston, this property offers not only a convenient lifestyle but also a promising investment prospect.
